Interface TcgProtocolBindingIdentifier

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TcgMProtocolBindingEnum, TcgTnccsProtocolBindingEnum, TcgTProtocolBindingEnum

    public interface TcgProtocolBindingIdentifier
    Extensible enumeration for protocol identifiers. A protocol identifier has always a label and a version.
